<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَإِنَّ هَذِهِ أُمَّتُكُمْ أُمَّةً وَاحِدَةً}</span> أَيْ: مِلَّةً وَاحِدَةً؛<span class="c5"> يَعْنِي:</span> الْإِسْلَامَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> مَنْ قَرَأَ: <span class="c3">{وَأَنَّ هَذِهِ}</span> بِفَتْحِ الْأَلِفِ فَالْمَعْنَى: لِأَنَّ هَذِه أمتكُم.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>